name: TokenTown
description:
This is a fundraiser to help save the town of Bridgeton which is for sale. Investing in TokenTown NFT gets you part ownership of our community owned town and your own lot. No passports necessary. All you need is minimum 1 TokenTown NFT. Will be announced on bitcointalk when we reach 10 sales.

Our town will not tolerate forced medical treatments and will be a haven for freedom!  

Thank you and hope to see you soon in our new town.
